  <sys:String x:Key="ModelSetupDescription" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">离线模型下载后会自动设为默认；实时与说话人模型可按需安装。</sys:String>
  <sys:String x:Key="ModelRequiredHint" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">至少安装一个离线或实时转写模型才能继续；也可以跳过引导，稍后再设置。</sys:String>
